# 12. Sliding Window Cheat Codes

---

## Cheat Code 1

Fixed Window

```java
sum += arr[end];
sum -= arr[end-k];
```

Remember this forever.

---

## Cheat Code 2

Longest Window

```java
while(invalid)
{
    shrink();
}
```

Then:

```java
ans = Math.max(ans, end-start+1);
```

---

## Cheat Code 3

Minimum Window

```java
while(valid)
{
    ans = Math.min(ans, end-start+1);
    shrink();
}
```

---

## Cheat Code 4

Distinct Elements

Use:

```java
HashMap<Integer,Integer>
```

Store frequency.

---

## Cheat Code 5

Characters

Use:

```java
int freq[] = new int[26];
```

Faster than HashMap.

