# 16. Advanced Patterns

---

## At Most K Distinct

```java
while(map.size() > k)
{
    shrink();
}
```

---

## Exactly K Distinct

Formula:

```java
Exactly(K)
=
AtMost(K)
-
AtMost(K-1)
```

Very important.

---

## Binary Array Problems

Examples:

```text
Max Consecutive Ones III
```

Use:

```java
while(zeros > k)
{
    shrink();
}
```

---

## Character Replacement

Maintain:

```java
maxFrequency
```

Condition:

```java
windowLength - maxFrequency > k
```

Shrink.

---

## Minimum Window Substring

Maintain:

```java
required count
```

Expand.

When valid:

```java
shrink aggressively
```

